# Invoice App Functionality

Source of truth for product behavior when planning or writing tests. UI locator details
live in `10-canvas-app-conventions`; Dataverse fields/API in `20-dataverse`.

## Invoice lifecycle

Happy path: **Create → Submit → Review → Approve → Send**

| Status | Meaning | Next Step (Overview) |
|--------|---------|----------------------|
| Draft | Editable, not submitted | (none or Edit) |
| Submitted | Awaiting review | **Review** |
| Reviewed | Awaiting approval | **Approve** |
| Approved | Waiting to send | **View** |
| Sent | Sent to customer | **View** |
| Flagged | Sent back for edit | **Edit** |
| Cancelled | Cancelled | — |
| Fail-Creation / Fail-Update / Fail-Flag / Fail-Approval / Fail-Review | Power Automate failure | **Report** |

Each workflow step runs a Power Automate flow (notify, update status, advance). Flow
failure → matching `Fail-*` status.

**Dashboard Failed** = all five `Fail-*` statuses where `dia_isReported` is blank
(unreported only).

### Invoice types

- **Non-adhoc (standard):** 1 invoice per billing period per project per contract.
  Second attempt → duplicate error. Available to PM and BDU.
- **Adhoc:** unlimited; **admin only**. Toggle **Adhoc Invoice** ON; forces **Brand New**.

## Billing / period filters (`dia_invoicedate`)

Not a calendar month for This/Last Month:

| Period | Range |
|--------|--------|
| This Month (current cycle) | 6th current month 00:00 → 5th next month 23:59 |
| Last Month | 6th previous → 5th current |
| Future Months | From 6th of **next** month onward |
| Quarter / Year to Date, Last Quarter / Year | **Calendar** boundaries (not billing cycle) |

Example (July 2026 This Month): 2026-07-06 → 2026-08-05.

## Screen: Dashboard (default landing)

- Header **Dashboard**; **+ Create Invoice**; **Region** filter (8 regions).
- Summary cards (This Month + Last Month; **excludes Cancelled**; region-filtered):
  Total Invoices, Total Partners, Total Project, Total Revenue.
- **Invoice Tasks** rows: Total Tasks, Drafts, Flagged, Submitted, Reviewed, Approved,
  Failed, Cancelled, Sent — each with a View … action.
- Task counts: **admin** = all invoices in billing cycle; **PM** = only where user is
  Submitter, Reviewer, or Approver.
- Regions: Australia, Colombia, India, Netherlands, North America, Saudi Arabia,
  South Korea, UAE.

## Screen: Invoice Overview

- Nav: **Invoice Overview**. **+ Create Invoice**.
- Radios **My Invoices** | **All Invoices** — **PM sees My Invoices only** (no radios).
- Period dropdown: This Month, Last Month, Quater to Date, Last Quater, Year to Date,
  Last Year, Future Months (match app typos **Quater**).
- Region filter; Search (Partner, Project, Invoice #).
- Table: Partner | Project | Invoice # | Action Pending with | Status | Next Step | ⋮
- Status badge colors: Submitted blue, Reviewed yellow/orange, Approved green,
  Flagged red, Draft grey, Sent purple; Fail-* as red text.
- Pagination at bottom.

## Screen: Create Invoice

- Radios: **Brand New** | **Start with last invoice** (pre-fills line items). Adhoc ON → Brand New.
- Toggles: **Adhoc Invoice** (default No, admin only); **Send Instantly** (urgent send notify).
- Invoice # / PO # disabled until after Submit (auto-populated).
- Invoice Date defaults to billing cycle **end**; Service Start/End default to cycle
  start/end; must fall within active **contract** period.
- Partner → filters Project. Line items: Product/Service | Description | Qty | Rate | Total.
  Product types: fixed locked rate | editable rate | enter both. Total = Qty × Rate.
  Add new item / delete row (img). Internal Notes optional rich text.
- Actions: Close, Save Draft (Draft, no flow), Submit (starts approval flow).
- Validation: Partner, Project, ≥1 line with Qty>0 and Rate>0, service dates in contract.

## Related Dataverse tables (context)

Accounts (partners), Projects (incl. Region), Contracts (valid service dates),
Products/Services, Security Roles (admin), Invoice Mail Lists (reviewer/approver per project).
